{
  "stem": "20021.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the only way to save him was for me to undertake that trip to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have a map there, which I could show you, if you wish me to go up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've prepared that map.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had a smuggler, whom I found out through that man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And incidentally, he found out about the smuggler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In other words, before this man-- his name is Marguilies-- before him, somebody by the name of Landau who had a son in Israel, got a letter from his son in Israel to contact a certain smuggler who will help him to get to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Landau went to Hungary, and sent a card to Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Marguilies, I arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Marguilies went to Hungary, and sent a card to me and told me, I arrived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But before he left, he told me the name of that smuggler and how to contact him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I contacted that smuggler.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Right?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he told me, here is the deal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It costs you that and that much money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Do you remember how much?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but it was a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, most people probably couldn't afford it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was fortunate I had the money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Plus, he said, look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All I'm doing for you is you never shake hands with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You never know me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If I'm ever asked, I never saw you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I never heard of you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Don't dare to come even close to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But keep watching.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'll be in this car.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You enter this car.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When I am supposed to jump, I'll pass to your car and make something-- I forgot the signal, the arranged signal was-- you get ready.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then you look out through the window.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
